## Unreal Engine 5
# Binaries (compiled executables and libraries)
**/Binaries/
*.dll
*.exe
*.pdb
*.lib
*.exp
*.obj

# Intermediate files (build artifacts, generated code)
**/Intermediate/
**/DerivedDataCache/

# Saved files (runtime data, logs, cache)
**/Saved/
**/Saved/**/*

# Build files (Visual Studio solution/project files - these are generated)
**/Build/
**/*.sln
**/*.vcxproj
**/*.vcxproj.filters
**/*.vcxproj.user

# Visual Studio files
**/.vs/
**/*.suo
**/*.user
**/*.userosscache
**/*.sln.docstates

# Content Browser cache
**/Content/**/*.tmp
**/Content/**/*.tmp.*

# Crash reports
**/CrashReports/

# Config (keep Config/ directory and non-user .ini files, ignore user-specific configs)
**/Config/*User*.ini
**/Config/*User*.ini.backup

# Logs
*.log
**/Logs/

# Web cache (CEF browser cache)
**/webcache_*/

# Autosave
**/Autosaves/

# Asset metadata (keep .uasset/.umap but ignore temp metadata)
**/*.uasset.tmp
**/*.umap.tmp

# Perforce (if used)
**/.p4ignore

# Rider
**/.idea/
**/*.iml

# XCode (if building on Mac)
**/DerivedData/
**/*.xcodeproj/*
!**/*.xcodeproj/project.pbxproj
!**/*.xcodeproj/xcshareddata/
**/*.xcworkspace/*
!**/*.xcworkspace/contents.xcworkspacedata
**/*.xcuserdata

# Test-generated assets (should not be tracked - tests create/cleanup these)
tests/**/Content/MCPTest/**/*.uasset
tests/**/Content/MCPTest/**/*.umap
tests/**/Content/*SmokeTest*.uasset
tests/**/Content/*SmokeTest*.umap
tests/**/Content/*Test*.uasset
tests/**/Content/*Test*.umap

# Smoke + demo runtime artifacts (recreated on every run; never source-of-truth)
tests/**/Content/MCP_Home.umap
tests/**/Content/MCP_SmokeScratch.umap
tests/**/Content/Demo/**/*.uasset
tests/**/Content/Demo/**/*.umap

# Note: The following WILL be tracked (as they should be):
# - *.uproject (project files)
# - Source/**/*.cpp, *.h, *.Build.cs, *.Target.cs (source code)
# - Config/*.ini (except *User*.ini - project configs are tracked)
# - Content/**/*.uasset, *.umap (content assets) - EXCEPT test-generated ones above
# - Plugins/**/*.uplugin (plugin files)
# - Any other project source files
ISSUE-AUDIT.md
CODE-SMELLS.md

